title: Vagina Shaming
description:
For millennia, people with vagina was told that there was something wrong with them (if they were even spoken about at all). Their vagina smelled wrong, looked wrong, it was too wet or not wet enough. This week on Sawbones, a reminder that your vagina is (almost always) just fine the way it is.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
